    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Hey @mthuret !\r\n\r\nAre you suggesting to use `connectInfiniteHits` in just the `ShowMoreResults` component instead of `createConnector`? I thought about seeing if I could use the `connectInfiniteHits` connector but I wasn't completely sure as to how to actually implement it. Not sure if you had an example for this but that would be helpful. Would I would wrap the `ShowMoreResults` component in `connectInfiniteHits` when I mount it in `SiteSearch`?\r\n\r\nYeah when I left the `ShowMoreResults` component mounted and tried to maintain the same behavior, clicking \"show more\" would initially show the correct results, but if I clicked \"back to results\" and then \"show more\" in a different category, it wouldn't update the results, so it would display the previous category results in the \"show more\" view. Not until I went back and clicked \"show more\" would it update so it seemed as if there was a lag maybe.\r\n",
