    "body": "Hey @tedlin182 \r\n\r\n1. The \"back to results\" link will have to reset the `page` to 0 for the given category. If you don't want to keep the query, then you should also clean up this one. \r\n2. You can keep a state inside your `<SiteSearch/>` component\r\n3. This is the part where I don't know :)\r\n\r\nAlso, please let me know if keeping in the state the page cursor works better than not unmouting your <ShowMoreResults/> component. ",
